WEBVTT

00:07.240 --> 00:13.050
♪ "L" is for the way
you look at me ♪

00:13.080 --> 00:19.250
♪ "o" is for the only one
i see ♪

00:19.290 --> 00:25.590
♪ "v" is
very, very extraordinary ♪

00:25.630 --> 00:31.630
♪ "e" is even more
than anyone that you adore can ♪

00:31.660 --> 00:36.600
♪ love is all
that I can give to you ♪

00:38.140 --> 00:41.610
♪ love is more than
just a game for two ♪

00:44.340 --> 00:47.450
♪ two in love can make it

00:47.480 --> 00:50.520
♪ take my heart
and please don't break it ♪

00:50.550 --> 00:54.590
♪ love was made for me and you

